snippet.title: Swap-Swap Panda - Puzzle Platformer for Mobile OUT NOW! (iOS/Android)
snippet.description:
PLAY Swap-Swap Panda ► https://bit.ly/2FAZdV7

Swap-Swap Panda is a cute puzzle platformer for mobile where you'll have to control and switch between two pandas with different skills in order to solve all the puzzles and complete the levels. The pandas are a chubby giant panda and a funny red panda, just with teamwork you'll be able to get through all the levels, by switching pandas and controlling one at a time.

Swap-Swap Panda is a cute adventure that will keep you engaged with many levels and replay values too as you need to collect all the stolen cupcakes in order to fully complete the game. If you enjoy funny pandas and epic fails this is the game for you so be sure to stick around this channel and check out the game as soon as it's available to iOS and Android. Thanks! #indiegame #platformer
